property_setters.name: Purchase Order Item-qty-description
property_setters.value:
Example 1: If ordering by roll: If 1 Roll = 2000 ea, set UOM to roll, set conversion factor to 2000.
Example 2: If ordering by lb: If 1 lb = .25 ea, set UOM to lb, set conversion factor to 0.25.
Example 3: If ordering by default UOM: set UOM to the default UOM, conversion factor to 1
